      "email",
      {
        "html": "<p>We often note how Wall Street moguls use union workers’ retirement savings to fund the war on workers. In <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/workers-are-funding-private-equitys-child-labor-exploitation/?utm_source=newsletter-email&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=newsletter-article\">today's featured story</a>, presented in full below, Andrew Perez reveals an especially bleak example of this dynamic: Private equity firms have repeatedly used government workers’ pension dollars to acquire and profit from businesses that outsource dangerous factory work — using undocumented immigrants and even children.</p>"
      }
    ],
